# My AI Agents

<% if @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") && !@current_user.stripe_billing_setup? %>
**Billing required** — [Set up billing](/billing) to create and run AI agents.

<% elsif @credit_balance_cents == 0 %>
**No credit balance** — [Add funds](/billing) to run AI agents.

<% end %>
<% if @ai_agents.any? %>
| Agent | Mode | Status | Latest Run |
|-------|------|--------|------------|
<% @ai_agents.each do |ai_agent| %>
<% latest_run = @latest_runs_by_ai_agent[ai_agent.id] %>
<% run_status = if latest_run
  case latest_run.status
  when "completed" then latest_run.success ? "Success" : "Failed"
  when "running" then "Running"
  when "queued" then "Queued"
  else latest_run.status.titleize
  end
else
  "No runs"
end %>
| [<%= ai_agent.display_name %>](/ai-agents/<%= ai_agent.handle %>)<%= " (archived)" if ai_agent.archived? %> | <%= ai_agent.internal_ai_agent? ? "Internal" : "External" %> | <%= ai_agent.archived? ? "Inactive" : "Active" %> | <%= run_status %> |
<% end %>
<% else %>
No AI agents yet. Create one using the `create_ai_agent` action at [/ai-agents/new](/ai-agents/new).
<% end %>
